d":"3101c63a400ef5bbe031b226a00dfb494ff9824f","tid":201770,"uid":64944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T08:00:47.000Z","msg":"老實講習總根本不痛不癢 唔會得閒理你班蟻民上網廢噏<br />\n反而班地方芝麻官又懶醒出黎捍衛皇室名聲"},{"pid":"fa4e310d04b01932ae7292108d33ad007f6f6946","tid":201770,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T08:02:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>習包子係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係指塊面發水麵包既意思，我見謝拉特都俾大6人叫包子。  又唔係咩人身攻擊，咁都要坐兩年。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28f3885b357b1906bf5a995d6314ce29c9760f4","tid":201770,"uid":22644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T08:07:01.000Z","msg":"好老實，國家領導人可以比你地d平民侮辱既咩<br />\n香港人成日誤解言論自由<br />\n支持祖國一黨專政"},{"pid":"5d8c30ac172ecb2f20ddeb760ca9271cdbca9c4f","tid":201770,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T09:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好老實，國家領導人可以比你地d平民侮辱既咩<br />\n香港人成日誤解言論自由<br />\n支持祖國一黨專政</blockquote><br />\n理得你真心定假膠 耕田啦屯門仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n春天到要播種啊"}]}